	<h1 id="rest-item cross selling">
		REST Item Cross Selling
	</h1>

	<p>Cross-selling is used to present additional items from the product range along with an item. These additional items can be necessary extensions or useful supplements to a customer's current selection. Replacement parts can also be offered as cross-selling items. A variation of this is dynamic cross-selling, where connections between items are created automatically based on the items that customers purchase together.</p>

